&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Scheduling&lt;/em&gt;: Work when it suits you, and take on as much or as little as you prefer.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Location&lt;/em&gt;: Set your own service area and claim jobs via the Proof app.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Technology&lt;/em&gt;: Use our app to accept work, track your earnings, and live chat with clients and Proof representatives.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How to Apply&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sign up in minutes and start earning within days.&lt;br&gt;You can apply to join the network as an independent Process Server directly on the Proof website or Mobile App. The sign-up process requires you to enter information such as your name, insurance, and driver&#39;s license number. You will also need to verify your identity and complete a quick background check.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;https://www.proofserve.com/become-a-process-server&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Certification&lt;/em&gt;: You must be a Licensed, Registered, or Certified Process Server if your state or county laws require it.&lt;br&gt;Must have a valid drivers license.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Technical Skills&lt;/em&gt;: Proficient with iPhone/iPad or Android devices and capable of using a mobile app.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Document Handling&lt;/em&gt;: Ability to scan and print documents. Free printing services are available via FedEx.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Experience&lt;/em&gt;: Prior experience in process serving or a related field (law enforcement, private investigations, etc.) is required, as Proof is not an employer and does not provide training. &lt;br&gt;National Association of Professional Process Servers (NAPPS) membership is preferred.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with Proof and take control of your schedule while providing essential services in the legal industry. Apply today to join other respected, independent Process Servers accepting work through the Proof platform.&lt;/p&gt;
